{"tid":651464,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"DC Comics討論 新書DC Nation #0網上免費任睇","createTime":"2018-05-03T06:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T05:17:09.000Z","uid":121471,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed756bf87d983909237c7ca05e95532f8021111d","tid":651464,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dccomics.com/reader/#/comics/437366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dccomics.com%2Freader%2F%23%2Fcomics%2F437366&d=v%2F4OAN7oD4ab9BaYZu%2Bh6zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8f66ad86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dccomics.com/reader/#/comics/437366</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/140807_603dfe35e9c758a78749ffc237e45523.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F140807_603dfe35e9c758a78749ffc237e45523.JPG&h=12296767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今個禮拜DC出左本新書 叫做DC Nation<br />\n第零期#0特別篇 收錄左三個故仔<br />\n三個都係黎緊呢個月DC故事既序幕 （包括Batman Catwoman婚禮）<br />\n雖然呢本野話就話要美金0.25 但係官網其實有電子版任睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/141300_0425a5f5b41ed382164841f093b30d92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F141300_0425a5f5b41ed382164841f093b30d92.jpg&h=70b8b0f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/141316_c72dde269fcc687cf3f5f7cb26f648ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F141316_c72dde269fcc687cf3f5f7cb26f648ca.jpg&h=7a9b9b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而下期第一期#1開始呢本書更會變成一本漫畫雜誌<br />\n有作家訪問 畫家手稿 漫畫消息 <del>Dan Didio廢話</del>等資訊<br />\n<br />\n睇完之後又真係幾吸引下 搞到我都心血來潮明知冇人理都開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ebed00ccb07be41e4f7a5e85e0d034d963bf67","tid":651464,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bleedingcool.com/2018/05/02/dc-nation-0-review-two-out-of-three-isnt-bad-plus-its-free-in-digital/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bleedingcool.com%2F2018%2F05%2F02%2Fdc-nation-0-review-two-out-of-three-isnt-bad-plus-its-free-in-digital%2F&d=v%2F4OAN7oD4ab9BaYZu%2Bh6zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=154991ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bleedingcool.com/2018/05/02/dc-nation-0-review-two-out-of-three-isnt-bad-plus-its-free-in-digital/</a><br />\n至於今期內容如何 呢篇review可以參考下<br />\nIn terms of getting me excited for the stories, the Batman and No Justice succeeded markedly more than Man of Steel, and that continues to worry me about the potential future of Brian Michael Bendis&rsquo; Superman and Action Comics."},{"pid":"8ba9c4be3ffafe4fb6cce26ec8427c9103f83106","tid":651464,"uid":70101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:32:04.000Z","msg":"Finally...."},{"pid":"f7740a0aa46afbe35bd5e611c3f8954b1af497c2","tid":651464,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:37:30.000Z","msg":"下期DC Nation #1 6/6出版<br />\n官網有冇任睇暫時未知<br />\n不過本實體書就係免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185498de20326ab86b2529e82af696caee1ff16b","tid":651464,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T13:20:19.000Z","msg":"Omega Titans冇乜特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6914ab432a1f11ade44d9a68e2fb1b5a0bcc88ac","tid":651464,"uid":121471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"Tom king終於寫返個正常joker"},{"pid":"5f7aa4801adad008fc725560204daad2410a0b63","tid":651464,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"多謝情報"},{"pid":"333dbc7e6934768bed459e69a51c70fb050fe7d4","tid":651464,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s