,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"Harley loves joker#1-2<br />\n兩期完故事<br />\n接住之前harley quinn主刊#17-25既back-up故事<br />\nBack-up故事講Harley出錯搞到joker要炸爆個舊巢<br />\n後來harley搵到人起新巢 點知就爭人三百萬<br />\n同時Gotham出現左一個新賊grison不停截joker想搶既目標<br />\n<br />\n#1-2交代grison原來係harley舊同學 佢將偷返黎既野俾返晒joker成功得寵<br />\n不過joker其實係計劃最後要搞掂grison<br />\n而harley到最後都係找唔到尾數 新巢又俾人炸爆埋<br />\n<br />\n充滿BTAS味道既故事 可以當係一個弱化版mad love咁睇<br />\nPaul dini除左幫harley加左個新宿敵外重交代左果兩隻鬣狗點黎<br />\nHarley內心對答好正 同joker亦係一慣btas相處方式<br />\n之後應該都會連埋back-up出合訂 鍾意dcau/btas既買得過<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/152424_ed3fdb83a5a48440f8cdbed68f2b3a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F152424_ed3fdb83a5a48440f8cdbed68f2b3a34.jpg&h=a463d7d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07d859be551061561b68866cea93f9047fb87b42","tid":651464,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dccomics.com/blog/2018/05/17/sufferin-succotash-more-dclooney-tunes-specials-coming-this-summer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dccomics.com%2Fblog%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2Fsufferin-succotash-more-dclooney-tunes-specials-coming-this-summer&d=v%2F4OAN7oD4ab9BaYZu%2Bh6zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b297c31a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dccomics.com/blog/2018/05/17/sufferin-succotash-more-dclooney-tunes-specials-coming-this-summer</a>"},{"pid":"4dbd0aa71033de50ccd51d76b2d6170b93774c20","tid":651464,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07d859be551061561b68866cea93f9047fb87b42","tid":651464,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dccomics.com/blog/2018/05/17/sufferin-succotash-more-dclooney-tunes-specials-coming-this-summer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dccomics.com%2Fblog%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2Fsufferin-succot